Digital Equipment Corp., Maynard, Mass., said it introduced a trade-in program for customers owning its VAX or Sun Microsystems Inc. workstations. 

Owners of Digital's VAXstation 2000 workstation may receive a $2,000 trade-in credit toward a VAXstation 3100 workstation, priced at $7,950. 

Owners of the Sun-3/50 workstation may receive a $2,000 credit toward the purchase of a VAXstation 3100 or DECstation 3100 workstation, priced at $11,900. 

Owners of Sun-3/60 workstation can receive a $4,000 trade-in credit toward the purchase of a VAXstation 3100 or DECstation 3100 workstation. 

